```markdown cell-id=intro
# Error Mapping Example

This notebook intentionally contains a compiler error so Zig-lab can show diagnostics mapped back to the notebook cell.
```

```zig cell-id=imports mode=decl
const std = @import("std");
```

```zig cell-id=broken mode=run depends-on=imports
const value = missing_value;
std.debug.print("value = {}\n", .{value});
```
